article_id:110,category_name:Events,title_name:Announcing event "Resplendent Refrain"!,image_path:,message:<div>The Resplendent Refrain raid event will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1543557600"></span></div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use Co-op Play to fight against the shadow raid boss!</div><div><br></div><div>Here&#39;s a sneak peek at the adventurers and dragon featured in this event!<br><br>■Lucretia</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/16feedd4929f635d9f4b4c3099ea10f3.png"></div><div>Called the songstress of the century, her ethereal voice captures the hearts of all who hear it.<br>Her voice has earned her renown across the continent, but rumors whisper that she has an equal talent for the slaying of fiends.<br><br></div><div>■Elias</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a182fa4e2d3dfecad39848c5c171f9e6.png"></div><div>A young boy from the Harmonia Choir. He boasts a heavenly voice, and expects the best from both himself and others when it comes to singing.<br>He likes sweet things a great deal, but fears this makes him seem a bit childish.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maritimus</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/aa1620125fcf6e1a45efbe5f53723d6e.png"></div><div>A dragon who protects the Harmonia Choir.<br>He has long lived in the town where they are based, where he is beloved by all. He enjoys being fashionable, and wears a bell the choir children gave him around his neck with pride.<br><br></div><div><br></div><div>■Notes:</div><div>1. You must clear Ch. 2 / 1-1 (Normal) to participate in Event Quests.</div><div>2. You must clear Ch. 2 / 2-1 (Normal) to participate in Co-op Play.</div><div>3. The event schedule and content may change without warning.</div><div><br></div><div>Thanks for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1543213800,update_time1543558226